<p class="tei tei-p" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.90em"><span style="font-size: 90%">326-07.—Coulommiers. Imp.</span> <span class="tei tei-hi" style="text-align: center"><span style="font-size: 90%; font-variant: small-caps">Paul
        BRODARD</span></span><span style="font-size: 90%">.—P4-07.</span></p>
</div>
